sources.title: Ladies Book Club - Full Movie
sources.description:
Bunny (Angell Conwell, 'Baby Boy') and Carlyle (Lyriq Bent, 'Acrimony') are roommates and have been best friends since college, but the attraction between them is undeniable, especially to their friends and families who use their book club meetings to spark a love connection.
